{"title":"川中小曲","authors":["关山月"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":2,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"川中小曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"关山月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北国还是冰天雪地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成都呵，却是一片葱绿；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我拂去旅途上的尘灰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深深吸一口清新空气！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿色的田野飘着红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处是高产田，高产地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一片片茁壮的嫩苗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引起远方来客的欣喜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间响起一声长笛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社社员开始休息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人群飞向竹林里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竹林响起青春曲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩霞照翠竹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翠竹多秀丽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少欢笑绕竹飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竹林里面好天地："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人在练歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人在唱戏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人在跳绳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人在下棋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人看书学文化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人提笔写诗句。……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个小娃子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想出个好主意："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光滑石板摆石桌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乒乓球儿桌上飞！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大娘满身力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉不服气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砍根藤条来拔河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老两口儿把武比！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少大娘来帮忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少老汉来助威，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田边溪水响淙淙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枝头鸟儿叫叽叽！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"川中田野春风起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风轻柔暖心底，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社无限好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民生活在幸福里。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}